 (Piano music)

353
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:46,000
 Yeah, Lord, help us to just continue to live our lives for you.

354
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:53,000
 It's all about you, Jesus.

355
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:55,000
 Thank you, Lord.

